title: Oracle Bell
description:
In the SNS App, high school students Suzu to understand the future only a little. She had lost her sense of justice in the past because of a certain event. The daily life of Suzu who thought so changes by disappearance of a classmate who had been unrequited…
 In the disappearance, more than 50 people seems to have been related to the mysterious disappeared...? With a mammoth population of more than 3,000,Suzu is looking for a hidden figure.
Who is the next victim, and who is the devil who is causing the shenanigans?
And what does Suzu get by touching them?

(By Hour of Lunacy)
